<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3787338>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Eutrichodesmus communicans sp. n., ♂ paratype from Fapon doline 3; A, habitus, lateral view; B, midbody segments, dorsal view; C, posterior part of body, dorsal view; D, same, ventral view; E, anterior part of body, ventrolateral view; F, same, front view. − Scale bars: A, 0.2 mm, B-F, 0.1 mm." ;
