<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3787342>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Eutrichodesmus communicans sp. n., ♂ paratype from Fapon doline 3; A, metatergal cerotegument and bisegmented setae; B, same with microvilli, lateral view; C, same with base of a bisegmented seta; D, legs, ventral view; E, gonopods, ventral view; F, left gonopod, dorsolateral view. − Scale bars: A, B, 0.01 mm, C, 0.005 mm, D, F, 0.05 mm." ;
